{"word":"H2620 - חָסָה - châçâh - khaw-saw' - Have hope","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חָסָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>châçâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khaw-saw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Have hope"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நம்பு, நம்பிபிரு, அண்டிக்கொள், ஒதுங்கு, வந்துஅடை, அடைக்கலம்புகு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"(Qal) to seek refuge, to flee for protection; to put trust in (God), to confide or to hope in (God) (figurative)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>flee</i> for protection (compare <a href=\"#/H982 - בָּטַח - bâṭach - baw-takh'/982\">H982</a>); figuratively to <i>confide</i> in: - have hope, make refuge, (put) trust."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2620 - חָסָה - châçâh - khaw-saw'/2620\">H2620</a>, <a href=\"#/H2621 - חֹסָה - Chôçâh - kho-saw'/2621\">H2621</a>, <a href=\"#/H2622 - חָסוּת - châçûwth - khaw-sooth'/2622\">H2622</a>, <a href=\"#/H4268 - מַחֲסֶה - machăçeh - makh-as-eh'/4268\">H4268</a>, <a href=\"#/H4271 - מַחְסֵיָה - Machçêyâh - makh-say-yaw'/4271\">H4271</a>"}]}